Bella Rossi returns to single match action. Her Tag Team was eliminated from the playoff picture so she has moved into single competition. This natural big titted grappler doesn't have many finesse moves or outstanding holds, but she has determination and big tits. This one is a brawler.
Rain Degrey is brawler number two, she has excellent stamina but lacks mat experience. This one hates losing and will give you 100% every second on the mat. If you're wrestling Rain you're in for a 24 minute war.
Bella's experience and wt advantage was too much for the rookie Rain to over come. After the match Bella picks up the smaller Rain and carries her to the bathroom, where she fuck and humiliates the helpless loser. Fun times.
title: Rain "Poison" DeGrey
